Dialogue: 10,0:00:04.41,0:00:05.81,Default2,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:06.21,0:00:09.32,Default2,,0,0,0,,Is it just me, or do we have an extra person in our group today?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:12.96,0:00:14.07,Default2,,0,0,0,,It's just you.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:14.07,0:00:15.73,Default2,,0,0,0,,That's impossible.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:15.73,0:00:18.05,Default2,,0,0,0,,What's this midget doing here?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:18.05,0:00:20.24,Default2,,0,0,0,,What does that have to do with you?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:20.24,0:00:25.58,Default2,,0,0,0,,Masaki-chan came to ask me about something that she didn't understand in class.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:25.86,0:00:26.83,Default2,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:28.90,0:00:31.91,Default2,,0,0,0,,I just need some stuff clarified.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:31.91,0:00:32.72,Default2,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:33.02,0:00:35.84,Default2,,0,0,0,,Since I'm at the top of our grade, I'll tutor you.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:36.31,0:00:38.93,Default2,,0,0,0,,I can explain it better than Shun.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:38.93,0:00:39.76,Default2,,0,0,0,,Let me see.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:39.76,0:00:41.06,Default2,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:41.06,0:00:43.19,Default2,,0,0,0,,I want Shun-chan to teach me!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:48.23,0:00:51.02,Default2,,0,0,0,,You have it all wrong! Kaname, you jerk! Four-eyes!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:51.02,0:00:52.53,Default2,,0,0,0,,Bookworm!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:52.53,0:00:53.07,Default2,,0,0,0,,Why, you!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:53.93,0:00:56.61,Default2,,0,0,0,,You're not the slightest bit cute.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:57.81,0:01:00.53,Default2,,0,0,0,,Masaki-chan's face was red.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:00.53,0:01:02.58,Default2,,0,0,0,,Does she have a cold?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:03.95,0:01:05.73,Default2,,0,0,0,,Maybe she's lovesick.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:06.68,0:01:10.45,Default2,,0,0,0,,Maybe she stayed up late studying math.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:10.45,0:01:11.90,Default2,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:11.90,0:01:16.09,Default2,,0,0,0,,She's desperately trying to solve an equation of love.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:16.44,0:01:18.69,Default2,,0,0,0,,Do you think she went to the hospital?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:18.69,0:01:20.81,Default2,,0,0,0,,You're the one who needs to go to the hospital.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:25.59,0:01:29.30,Default2,,0,0,0,,A student is transferring to our class soon.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:29.30,0:01:31.53,Default2,,0,0,0,,Apparently, he's returning from abroad.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:31.53,0:01:32.89,Default2,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:34.29,0:01:37.24,Default2,,0,0,0,,There's been a lot of activity around us lately.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:39.79,0:01:42.29,Default2,,0,0,0,,We met an awkward first-year,
Dialogue: 10,0:01:42.29,0:01:46.73,Default2,,0,0,0,,and now, we're going to meet an unknown transfer student.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:18.27,0:03:21.72,Default2,,0,0,0,,I'd like to introduce the transfer student.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:22.07,0:03:23.97,Default2,,0,0,0,,I'm Tachibana Chizuru.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:23.97,0:03:25.22,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\an8}He's blond!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:25.22,0:03:26.57,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\an8}A blondie!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:24.29,0:03:26.19,Default2,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:26.86,0:03:28.47,Default2,,0,0,0,,If you have any questions,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:28.47,0:03:31.49,Default2,,0,0,0,,ask your class representative, Tsukahara-kun.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:32.30,0:03:35.26,Default2,,0,0,0,,Tachibana-kun, your desk is over there.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:35.26,0:03:36.36,Default2,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:38.22,0:03:39.40,Default2,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:39.40,0:03:42.43,Default2,,0,0,0,,I hope you'll share your textbook when I forget mine.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:43.31,0:03:44.91,Default2,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:46.34,0:03:47.48,Default2,,0,0,0,,Likewise.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:51.34,0:03:53.36,Default2,,0,0,0,,I'm taking attendance.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:53.36,0:03:54.21,Default2,,0,0,0,,Aoto.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:54.21,0:03:54.67,Default2,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:54.67,0:03:55.60,Default2,,0,0,0,,Akaishi.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:55.60,0:03:56.17,Default2,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:56.17,0:03:57.21,Default2,,0,0,0,,Akiyama.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:57.21,0:03:58.04,Default2,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:03.99,0:04:05.14,Default2,,0,0,0,,What a shock!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:05.45,0:04:07.55,Default2,,0,0,0,,You're that kid, aren't you?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:07.55,0:04:09.14,Default2,,0,0,0,,No, um...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:07.40,0:04:09.14,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hey, Tachibana-kun...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:09.14,0:04:12.89,Default2,,0,0,0,,We played together at that park!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:13.13,0:04:13.74,Default2,,0,0,0,,Didn't we?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:13.74,0:04:15.90,Default2,,0,0,0,,That was such a long time ago.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:16.11,0:04:18.23,Default2,,0,0,0,,Small world, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:18.23,0:04:19.80,Default2,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:19.80,0:04:21.99,Default2,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:29.70,0:04:30.74,Default2,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:31.07,0:04:33.42,Default2,,0,0,0,,You stand here during every break.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:33.42,0:04:37.42,Default2,,0,0,0,,Someone keeps making strange advances if I hang out over there.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:37.42,0:04:42.76,Default2,,0,0,0,,It's really unusual for someone to approach you head-on.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:42.76,0:04:45.80,Default2,,0,0,0,,It's not so much "head-on" as from the right.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:45.80,0:04:47.26,Default2,,0,0,0,,Found you!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:51.59,0:04:53.36,Default2,,0,0,0,,A clone?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:53.36,0:04:55.68,Default2,,0,0,0,,We're twins.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:55.68,0:04:58.16,Default2,,0,0,0,,I'm his older brother, Yuuta.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:58.16,0:05:01.65,Default2,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're just his twin brother.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:01.65,0:05:04.15,Default2,,0,0,0,,How do you two know each other?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:04.46,0:05:08.22,Default2,,0,0,0,,In his delusional world, \Nwe used to know each other.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:08.22,0:05:09.41,Default2,,0,0,0,,That's not it!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:09.41,0:05:11.66,Default2,,0,0,0,,We really do know each other!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:11.66,0:05:14.37,Default2,,0,0,0,,There you are.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:14.37,0:05:17.29,Default2,,0,0,0,,I thought I'd give you a tour of the school.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:17.29,0:05:18.55,Default2,,0,0,0,,Are you free?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:20.26,0:05:21.51,Default2,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:21.92,0:05:24.65,Default2,,0,0,0,,Tsukahara Kaname. I'm in your class.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:24.65,0:05:28.28,Default2,,0,0,0,,Our teacher told you to come to me if you have any questions.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:28.28,0:05:31.14,Default2,,0,0,0,,I'll ask Yukki, so don't sweat it.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:31.41,0:05:33.44,Default2,,0,0,0,,Yukki?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:33.44,0:05:37.19,Default2,,0,0,0,,He calls you Yukki?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:37.19,0:05:41.45,Default2,,0,0,0,,We're old friends, so it's an affectionate nickname.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:42.65,0:05:47.65,Default2,,0,0,0,,I'll affectionately call you, my classmate...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:47.97,0:05:49.03,Default2,,0,0,0,,Four-eyes.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:49.95,0:05:52.62,Default2,,0,0,0,,That name's clearly full of animosity!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:52.62,0:05:53.92,Default2,,0,0,0,,Now, now...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:54.33,0:05:56.76,Default2,,0,0,0,,You two must really be friends.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:56.76,0:05:59.90,Default2,,0,0,0,,First thing you do is piss me off.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:59.90,0:06:02.84,Default2,,0,0,0,,Birds of a feather flock together.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:02.84,0:06:07.84,Default2,,0,0,0,,But Yuuki's acting like the transfer student has confused him with someone else.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:07.84,0:06:12.35,Default2,,0,0,0,,A stranger's a stranger. See you later.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:12.35,0:06:13.60,Default2,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:15.02,0:06:16.58,Default2,,0,0,0,,He's so cold.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:16.58,0:06:20.31,Default2,,0,0,0,,I feel like he used to be a lot nicer.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:20.31,0:06:21.81,Default2,,0,0,0,,Nice?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:21.81,0:06:23.98,Default2,,0,0,0,,That's definitely not him.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:23.98,0:06:27.86,Default2,,0,0,0,,I'm sure he's just embarrassed to see his old friend again.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:27.95,0:06:31.87,Default2,,0,0,0,,I have to make Yukki acknowledge me!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:32.14,0:06:33.64,Default2,,0,0,0,,Hold up, Yu—
Dialogue: 10,0:06:43.44,0:06:45.59,Default2,,0,0,0,,Who's that? His girlfriend?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:45.59,0:06:47.13,Default2,,0,0,0,,That's not his girlfriend.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:47.13,0:06:49.01,Default2,,0,0,0,,He's not even a girl.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:49.01,0:06:50.97,Default2,,0,0,0,,How dare you say that?!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:50.97,0:06:53.76,Default2,,0,0,0,,I know she's a little flat chested,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:53.76,0:06:58.27,Default2,,0,0,0,,but it's our job as men to appreciate them anyway!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:58.99,0:07:01.02,Default2,,0,0,0,,Hey, girlfriend!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:01.82,0:07:02.85,Default2,,0,0,0,,Where did they go?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:02.85,0:07:05.39,Default2,,0,0,0,,Huh? Hey, hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:06.11,0:07:09.78,Default2,,0,0,0,,I told you that he isn't a girl.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:09.78,0:07:16.54,Default2,,0,0,0,,Yuuta, words are meaningless unless the other person listens.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:21.54,0:07:23.38,Default2,,0,0,0,,He's not a girl.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:23.38,0:07:26.63,Default2,,0,0,0,,There you go again, saying the same thing as your brother.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:26.94,0:07:29.92,Default2,,0,0,0,,That girl was so cute.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:30.63,0:07:32.51,Default2,,0,0,0,,It's a shame I didn't get a chance to talk to her.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:34.23,0:07:36.81,Default2,,0,0,0,,It's not like I was afraid of being shot down.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:37.21,0:07:40.06,Default2,,0,0,0,,She seemed to be heading to the locker room.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:41.31,0:07:43.56,Default2,,0,0,0,,Amazing. Did you see that?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:46.71,0:07:47.75,Default2,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:49.07,0:07:51.57,Default2,,0,0,0,,You really don't remember me?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:54.26,0:07:55.57,Default2,,0,0,0,,Remember you?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:55.93,0:07:57.83,Default2,,0,0,0,,I have no idea who you are.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:57.83,0:08:00.89,Default2,,0,0,0,,Girls don't like overly persistent guys.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:00.89,0:08:02.58,Default2,,0,0,0,,But you're a boy...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:13.70,0:08:15.59,Default2,,0,0,0,,I was wondering who you were.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:15.59,0:08:19.17,Default2,,0,0,0,,I didn't recognize you without your glasses.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:20.24,0:08:24.48,Default2,,0,0,0,,With your hair like that, I thought you were Yuuta for a minute.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:28.37,0:08:30.87,Default2,,0,0,0,,Oh, my bangs.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:34.86,0:08:36.43,Default2,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:40.09,0:08:41.16,Default2,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:41.16,0:08:43.41,Default2,,0,0,0,,I told you...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:43.41,0:08:46.79,Default2,,0,0,0,,Hey, that kid you played with once...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:46.79,0:08:48.29,Default2,,0,0,0,,You remember?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:49.07,0:08:50.80,Default2,,0,0,0,,Could it have been Yuuta?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:50.80,0:08:51.88,Default2,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:51.88,0:08:55.30,Default2,,0,0,0,,You might have us confused. We do look the same.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:56.74,0:08:59.15,Default2,,0,0,0,,You are identical, but...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:00.33,0:09:03.27,Default2,,0,0,0,,I'm pretty sure it was Yukki.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:14.66,0:09:15.78,Default2,,0,0,0,,Still not done?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:16.17,0:09:17.28,Default2,,0,0,24,,Not yet.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:17.57,0:09:19.62,Default2,,0,0,24,,You're just going to end up buying it.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:19.62,0:09:22.74,Default2,,0,0,24,,I won't know if it's worth buying a copy
Dialogue: 10,0:09:22.74,0:09:25.04,Default2,,0,0,24,,for archival purposes until I've read it.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:25.04,0:09:28.00,Default2,,0,0,24,,You should stop doing that.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:28.41,0:09:32.46,Default2,,0,0,24,,Books are made to be read.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:33.58,0:09:38.21,Default2,,0,0,0,,You're not telling me that you know how this book feels, are you?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:38.21,0:09:39.84,Default2,,0,0,0,,I do understand.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:39.84,0:09:41.40,Default2,,0,0,0,,Now hurry up and buy it.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:43.02,0:09:45.10,Default2,,0,0,0,,Now I'm kind of jealous.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:45.10,0:09:47.23,Default2,,0,0,0,,I'll keep reading until I understand it, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:47.82,0:09:49.61,Default2,,0,0,0,,That's not what I wanted.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:50.86,0:09:54.36,Default2,,0,0,0,,That kid really is blond, isn't he?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:54.78,0:09:58.49,Default2,,0,0,0,,From a distance, he looks like he's wearing a straw hat.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:58.74,0:10:00.74,Default2 - Italic,,0,0,0,,Could it have been Yuuta?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:01.25,0:10:03.49,Default2,,0,0,0,,I have to find a way...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:06.95,0:10:08.65,Default2,,0,0,0,,This one again?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:11.78,0:10:13.13,Default2,,0,0,0,,This...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:13.13,0:10:15.71,Default2,,0,0,0,,If you're going to buy it, just buy it already.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:15.71,0:10:19.01,Default2,,0,0,0,,I can always buy manga volumes later,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:19.01,0:10:22.24,Default2,,0,0,0,,but it's hard to find magazines long after they've been published.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:24.01,0:10:25.64,Default2,,0,0,0,,Hold on!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:26.52,0:10:28.69,Default2,,0,0,0,,Did you follow us?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:28.69,0:10:31.40,Default2,,0,0,0,,Do you remember the toy I gave you?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:31.40,0:10:32.27,Default2,,0,0,0,,What toy?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:32.27,0:10:33.65,Default2,,0,0,0,,I gave you one!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:33.65,0:10:37.11,Default2,,0,0,0,,I don't remember what it was, but I'm sure it was cool.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:37.11,0:10:38.11,Default2,,0,0,0,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:38.11,0:10:39.70,Default2,,0,0,0,,"Who knows?"
Dialogue: 10,0:10:39.70,0:10:41.95,Default2,,0,0,0,,I did! I gave it to you!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:41.95,0:10:44.03,Default2,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:44.03,0:10:47.14,Default2,,0,0,0,,Was this in front of the park?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:48.23,0:10:53.09,Default2,,0,0,0,,My memory's pretty fuzzy, so I don't remember the details.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:53.09,0:10:56.59,Default2,,0,0,0,,I think someone gave me something like that.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:56.59,0:10:58.63,Default2,,0,0,0,,What? Then...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:58.63,0:11:02.45,Default2,,0,0,0,,Oh, but I don't remember you.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:11.46,0:11:12.77,Default2,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:12.77,0:11:15.15,Default2,,0,0,0,,I see. So it was Yuuta.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:15.15,0:11:17.12,Default2,,0,0,0,,I don't remember him at all, though.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:17.12,0:11:19.70,Default2,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:19.70,0:11:23.78,Default2,,0,0,0,,At least he's stopped bothering you.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:24.14,0:11:24.78,Default2,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:25.85,0:11:26.79,Default2,,0,0,0,,So small.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:26.79,0:11:29.29,Default2,,0,0,0,,Who are you guys talking about?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:29.73,0:11:30.83,Default2,,0,0,0,,That's all for today.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:30.83,0:11:34.54,Default2,,0,0,0,,Students on day duty please bring the class register to the faculty office later.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:05.27,0:12:10.33,Default2,,0,0,0,,Everyone I ask says they don't remember me.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:10.33,0:12:13.36,Default2,,0,0,0,,Maybe I'm actually a fictional character.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:14.31,0:12:16.92,Default2,,0,0,0,,What're you laughing at, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:16.92,0:12:18.30,Default2,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:18.30,0:12:21.09,Default2,,0,0,0,,You just smirked at us, didn't you?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:21.09,0:12:23.36,Default2,,0,0,0,,No, I...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:26.39,0:12:29.64,Default2,,0,0,0,,You're too cocky for a nobody.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:29.64,0:12:31.64,Default2,,0,0,0,,What's with this hair?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:32.02,0:12:34.39,Default2,,0,0,0,,You think this blond hair looks cool?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:35.11,0:12:37.27,Default2,,0,0,0,,Don't get so excited over this crap!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:44.49,0:12:47.49,Default2,,0,0,0,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:48.34,0:12:50.20,Default2,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:51.33,0:12:54.50,Default2,,0,0,0,,Yuutan and Yukki.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:54.50,0:12:56.42,Default2,,0,0,0,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:56.42,0:12:59.13,Default2,,0,0,0,,There sure are a lot of you against just one opponent.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:59.34,0:13:02.21,Default2,,0,0,0,,No, no. That's not what this is.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:02.21,0:13:03.51,Default2,,0,0,0,,I was just playing around.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:05.18,0:13:07.09,Default2,,0,0,0,,Who do you think you are?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:07.31,0:13:09.10,Default2,,0,0,0,,Say something!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:09.91,0:13:11.23,Default2,,0,0,0,,I'm finished.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:12.02,0:13:13.65,Default2,,0,0,0,,Where's the second volume?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:14.42,0:13:19.18,Default2,,0,0,0,,Huh? Um, it's probably in my bag or my locker or...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:19.18,0:13:23.11,Default2,,0,0,0,,What? How am I supposed to know from that?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:24.22,0:13:26.91,Default2,,0,0,0,,Let me borrow this guy for a minute.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:26.91,0:13:28.45,Default2,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:28.45,0:13:30.58,Default2,,0,0,0,,I'll return him later.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:30.58,0:13:31.28,Default2,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:31.28,0:13:32.49,Default2,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:32.49,0:13:34.33,Default2,,0,0,0,,He's busy with...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:32.77,0:13:34.33,Default2,,0,0,0,,It's the Principal.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:35.10,0:13:36.37,Default2,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:36.37,0:13:38.08,Default2,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:15.75,0:14:17.58,Default2,,0,0,0,,I'm bored.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:17.58,0:14:21.71,Default2,,0,0,0,,It's summer, but Yuuta's sick.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:21.71,0:14:23.56,Default2,,0,0,0,,What am I going to do by myself?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:28.71,0:14:32.76,Default2,,0,0,0,,His head's yellow, like a straw hat.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:32.76,0:14:35.27,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come on, play with me!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:35.27,0:14:37.52,Default2,,0,0,0,,What language is that?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:39.51,0:14:41.52,Default2,,0,0,0,,You want to play together?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:47.03,0:14:50.91,Default2,,0,0,0,,Um, what's your name?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:50.91,0:14:54.53,Default2,,0,0,0,,My mom told me not to talk to strangers.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:57.54,0:14:59.03,Default2,,0,0,0,,He doesn't understand me.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:04.67,0:15:06.53,Default2,,0,0,0,,Another nobody.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:07.83,0:15:09.17,Default2,,0,0,0,,Do you want to try?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:11.18,0:15:12.47,Default2,,0,0,0,,Put it in.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:15.81,0:15:17.13,Default2,,0,0,0,,And turn it.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:21.50,0:15:24.64,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh, really cool!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:24.64,0:15:27.69,Default2 - Italic,,0,0,0,,Hero Yamato complete version!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:29.81,0:15:33.20,Default2,,0,0,0,,No, I have to get it on my own.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:34.03,0:15:39.12,Default2,,0,0,0,,More importantly, why am I here with some weird kid...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:44.03,0:15:49.27,Default2 - Italic,,0,0,0,,I don't mind playing without talking, though.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:50.49,0:15:51.88,Default2,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:54.03,0:15:55.35,Default2,,0,0,0,,Oh, no.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:55.65,0:15:57.39,Default2,,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:58.10,0:16:02.10,Default2,,0,0,0,,You've done it now, you jerk.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:02.10,0:16:04.11,Default2,,0,0,0,,Now it's my turn.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:20.46,0:16:22.37,Default2 - Italic,,0,0,0,,Almost there.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:38.43,0:16:40.35,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Cool!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:13.77,0:17:15.05,Default2,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:19.17,0:17:21.37,Default2,,0,0,0,,W-Wait here.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:21.85,0:17:25.52,Default2,,0,0,0,,I-I'll go get an adult!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:43.85,0:17:44.95,Default2,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:48.38,0:17:53.01,Default2 - Italic,,0,0,0,,I guess he can't understand even if I apologize.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:59.27,0:18:06.14,Default2,,0,0,0,,Yuuta-chan's finally better, and now you're sick.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:06.14,0:18:08.27,Default2,,0,0,0,,Where's Yuuta?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:08.27,0:18:10.94,Default2,,0,0,0,,He's out shopping.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:10.94,0:18:15.24,Default2,,0,0,0,,It's a shame you can't play outside in this beautiful weather.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:17.74,0:18:19.05,Default2,,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:22.30,0:18:23.91,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:27.82,0:18:30.04,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why are you ignoring me?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:30.04,0:18:31.79,Default2 - Italic,,0,0,0,,What does he want?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:31.79,0:18:34.96,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What you doing? I'll leave you behind!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:34.96,0:18:36.57,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wait for me!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:44.86,0:18:46.09,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thanks!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:53.66,0:18:55.08,Default2,,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:55.78,0:18:58.71,Default2,,0,0,0,,I bought some apple juice.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:59.57,0:19:01.03,Default2,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:01.94,0:19:04.93,Default2,,0,0,0,,And I got you a gift.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:06.06,0:19:07.70,Default2,,0,0,0,,Hero Yamato!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:07.70,0:19:10.80,Default2,,0,0,0,,No fair, Yuuta. You used the toy machine?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:10.80,0:19:12.45,Default2,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:13.29,0:19:16.67,Default2,,0,0,0,,When I passed by the park,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:16.67,0:19:21.80,Default2,,0,0,0,,this blond-haired kid came up to me and gave me this.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:22.29,0:19:25.81,Default2,,0,0,0,,I couldn't understand anything he said, though.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:25.81,0:19:30.93,Default2,,0,0,0,,I'm not interested in that stuff, so you can have it.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:32.69,0:19:33.94,Default2,,0,0,0,,Yuuki?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:36.94,0:19:39.45,Default2,,0,0,0,,I wanted to get it myself...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:41.77,0:19:46.05,Default2 - Italic,,0,0,0,,My words melted away in the sunlight of that childhood day without reaching him.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:46.91,0:19:51.60,Default2 - Italic,,0,0,0,,Only the blue summer sky saw what happened.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:10.61,0:20:16.27,Default2,,0,0,0,,Yukki, you were the one whom I played with on that day.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:21.35,0:20:23.77,Default2,,0,0,0,,You should just say it was Yuuta.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:27.37,0:20:31.37,Default2,,0,0,0,,You and Yuutan aren't clones.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:31.37,0:20:35.38,Default2,,0,0,0,,You read manga in the face of violence.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:38.15,0:20:41.21,Default2,,0,0,0,,And I don't apologize for hurting others.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:41.79,0:20:43.22,Default2,,0,0,0,,You don't?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:44.18,0:20:45.55,Default2,,0,0,0,,I'm talking about what happened to you.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:47.18,0:20:48.81,Default2,,0,0,0,,Oh, that.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:50.05,0:20:56.06,Default2,,0,0,0,,I guess it did hurt, but I wouldn't have wanted you to apologize.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:57.34,0:21:01.15,Default2,,0,0,0,,I really had fun.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:01.15,0:21:06.97,Default2,,0,0,0,,I had fun and I was happy, so an apology is a little...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:08.35,0:21:09.58,Default2,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:19.79,0:21:23.45,Default2,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't learn German just to apologize.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:24.30,0:21:25.72,Default2,,0,0,0,,It'd be too much work.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:34.91,0:21:36.44,Default2,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:36.44,0:21:39.94,Default2,,0,0,0,,Is it just me, or do we have {\i1}another{\i0} extra member today?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:39.94,0:21:41.82,Default2,,0,0,0,,Her name's Matsuoka-san?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:41.82,0:21:43.82,Default2,,0,0,0,,Your girlfriend is cute, isn't she?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:43.82,0:21:47.82,Default2,,0,0,0,,I heard she's good friends with all of you and usually comes up here, too!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:47.82,0:21:49.62,Default2,,0,0,0,,Who's Matsuoka-san?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:49.62,0:21:51.33,Default2,,0,0,0,,Furthermore, who are you?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:53.01,0:21:54.83,Default2,,0,0,0,,I thought you'd be here.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:55.35,0:21:57.25,Default2,,0,0,0,,It's Matsuoka-san.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:59.33,0:22:01.34,Default2,,0,0,0,,Matsuoka-san...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:02.96,0:22:04.59,Default2,,0,0,0,,You're late.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:04.97,0:22:07.39,Default2,,0,0,0,,I had to fill in the class register.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:14.22,0:22:15.18,Default2,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:17.39,0:22:19.60,Default2,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you, Matsuoka-{\i1}kun{\i0}.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:19.60,0:22:22.28,Default2,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:24.90,0:22:25.94,Default2,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:27.05,0:22:28.36,Default2,,0,0,0,,Are you ok?!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:28.36,0:22:30.95,Default2,,0,0,0,,Don't wake him, Shun.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:30.95,0:22:35.04,Default2,,0,0,0,,Don't ever wake him. He never shuts up.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:35.04,0:22:37.37,Default2,,0,0,0,,I tried to tell him you weren't a girl.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:37.37,0:22:40.96,Default2,,0,0,0,,Words really are powerful things.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:17.21,0:24:18.50,Default2,,0,0,0,,Next time,
Dialogue: 10,0:24:18.50,0:24:20.05,Default2,,0,0,0,,Noisy Medicine
